    "date": "2011-10-07T17:39:05Z",
    "text": "Corporate Assets Should be used to Hire Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to impose on domestic corporations in taxable years beginning in 2011 or 2012\u00a0an additional 40% tax on the excess of their retained earnings over their average retained earnings for the preceding 3 taxable years.\u00a0 Exempts certain corporations from such tax, including corporations\u00a0with retained earnings of less than $5 million in a taxable year."
